# Steps to install SASS

1. Installed NVM (Node Version Manager):
   $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Exited and reopened the terminal to load NVM.

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16:
   $ nvm install 20.16.0
   $ nvm use 20.16.0

4. Verified Node and npm installation:
   $ node -v
   $ npm -v

5. Installed the latest stable version of SASS:
   $ npm install sass

6. Verified SASS installation:
   $ npx sass --version
